          <div class="community-sections">
            <div class="community-section">
              <h3>Kings Island Entertainment District</h3>
              <p>
                The heart of Mason's tourism economy, requiring specialized concrete solutions that 
                support high-volume entertainment and hospitality operations.
              </p>
              <ul>
