                <li>Distribution and logistics facilities</li>
                <li>Healthcare and professional services</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Process Excellence -->
      <section class="process-section">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>Our Mason Concrete Coating Process</h2>
          
          <div class="process-steps">
            <div class="process-step">
              <div class="step-number">1</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Property Evaluation</h3>
                <p>
                  Comprehensive assessment of your Mason property, considering local conditions, 
                  usage requirements, and community standards for optimal solution development.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="process-step">
              <div class="step-number">2</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Customized Design</h3>
                <p>
                  Personalized coating system selection based on your specific needs, aesthetic 
                  preferences, and Mason's community character and requirements.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="process-step">
              <div class="step-number">3</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Professional Installation</h3>
                <p>
                  Expert application using proven techniques and premium materials, with careful 
                  attention to Mason's quality standards and neighborhood considerations.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="process-step">
              <div class="step-number">4</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Quality Assurance</h3>
                <p>
                  Thorough inspection and customer satisfaction verification, ensuring your Mason 
                  installation meets our quality standards and your expectations.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Customer Testimonials -->
      <section class="testimonials">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>Mason Customer Experiences</h2>
          
          <div class="testimonials-grid">
            <div class="testimonial">
              <div class="testimonial-content">
                <p>
                  "Our hotel needed flooring that could handle the constant traffic of Kings Island 
                  visitors while maintaining a luxury appearance. The results have been outstanding - 
                  beautiful, durable, and much easier to maintain than our previous surfaces."
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="testimonial-author">
                <strong>Hotel Manager</strong> - Kings Island Area
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="testimonial">
              <div class="testimonial-content">
                <p>
                  "The garage floor transformation exceeded our expectations. Living in Mason with an 
                  active family, we needed something that could handle everything from sports equipment 
                  to DIY projects. Perfect solution with beautiful results."
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="testimonial-author">
                <strong>Jennifer & Mark S.</strong> - Mason Homeowners
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="testimonial">
              <div class="testimonial-content">
                <p>
                  "Our technology facility required specialized ESD-safe flooring for our clean rooms. 
                  The expertise and attention to detail ensured we met all requirements while creating 
